{
  "texts": [
    "With the retrieved PubMed IDs, we used the web scraping tool BeautifulSoup [44], a Python library, to extract titles and abstracts from the papers on PubMed.",
    "The set of abstracts obtained using the selected keywords is further processed to eliminate those papers which do not contain a reference to the organism, either in its full form, or as abbreviations.",
    "Sentence tokenization.",
    "We split the final set of abstracts into individual sentences using Punkt sentence tokenizer from the Natural Language Toolkit (NLTK) [45].",
    "Punkt is a pretrained unsupervised machine learning model designed for detecting sentence boundaries."
  ]
}